text: Laura Wissink (born 7 July 1997) is a Dutch softball player. Wissink plays with Tex Town Tigers She is member of the Netherlands women's national softball team. With the national team she became European champion at the 2022 Women's Softball European Championship. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch softball players Category:People from Enschede Category:Sportspeople from Overijssel Category:Sportswomen
